com.nevermindsoftware.urlparser.tld

Interface TLDSource

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CachedTLDSource, ClasspathTLDSource

    public TLDSource

    Interface specifying a provider of TLD SuffixRules. It should return a list of SuffixRules. Caching is down to the implementation and is not required, but the TLDSource will be queried on each usage of the parse methods of a UrlParser
